# ServeLink Landing Page — Cursor Rules

You are restyling the ServeLink landing page (Next.js + Tailwind) to match the "Heritage Tech" design system defined in DESIGN.md at the project root.

## Color Migration Map
Replace ALL old colors with Heritage Tech equivalents:

OLD → NEW:
- teal (#1B6B7B, #145661) → primary (#00342a) or primary-container (#004d3f)
- orange (#E85D04, bg-orange, orange-dark) → secondary-container (#fecc00)
- dark blue (#1a2744, #243556) → primary (#00342a)
- gray-50, gray-100 backgrounds → surface (#fcf9f8) or surface-container-low (#f6f3f2)
- pure black text → on-surface (#1b1b1b)
- white/15, white/10 glass effects → keep but ensure they work on the new green gradient

## Tailwind Class Replacements
- bg-teal-* → bg-[#00342a] or bg-[#004d3f]
- text-teal-* → text-[#00342a]
- bg-orange → bg-[#fecc00]
- text-orange → text-[#fecc00]
- hover:bg-orange-dark → hover:bg-[#d4ad00]
- border-teal-* → border-[#00342a]
- bg-gray-50 → bg-[#fcf9f8]
- bg-gray-100 → bg-[#f6f3f2]

## Typography
- Headlines: Plus Jakarta Sans (add via Google Fonts if not present)
- Body: Manrope
- Emphasize scale difference between headlines and body

## Component Rules
- Buttons: rounded-full with 1.5rem radius. Primary = bg-[#00342a] text-white. CTA = bg-[#fecc00] text-[#1b1b1b]
- Cards: no borders, use tonal layering (bg-[#f6f3f2] on bg-[#fcf9f8])
- Glass effects: 80% opacity + backdrop-blur-xl on primary background
- No 1px dividers — use spacing or alternating surface colors
- Shadows: use on-surface at 6% opacity

## Rules
1. Do NOT change any functionality, translations, API calls, or component structure
2. Only update colors, typography, spacing, and visual styling
3. Keep all i18n (EN/FR) support intact
4. Keep all animations — just update the colors they use
5. The globals.css has already been updated — use the CSS variables defined there
6. Maintain all responsive breakpoints
